Ya.

526
00:41:33,709 --> 00:41:36,409
Surat kabar resmi mengatakan hakim wilayah yang baru adalah

527
00:41:36,679 --> 00:41:37,809
Baek

528
00:41:38,449 --> 00:41:39,510
Yi

529
00:41:40,010 --> 00:41:41,150
Hyun.

530
00:41:42,319 --> 00:41:45,049
