531
00:41:46,449 --> 00:41:47,449
Ibu.

532
00:41:48,959 --> 00:41:52,230
Kita tidak perlu mengkhawatirkan Yi Hyun lagi.

533
00:41:53,459 --> 00:41:55,230
Kita harus merayakannya.

534
00:41:55,429 --> 00:41:59,600
