709
00:56:40,380 --> 00:56:41,449
Silakan pergi.

710
00:56:41,449 --> 00:56:43,679
Aku sudah memperingatkanmu.

711
00:56:43,749 --> 00:56:45,790
Anda lebih hina daripada binatang.

